            <title>[CASSANDRA-7189] Repair hang when specified CF does not exist</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7189</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;StorageService#getValidColumnFamilies throws IllegalArgumentException when given CF name does not exist.&lt;br/&gt;
We need to catch that in order to prevent repair from hanging.&lt;br/&gt;
(2.1+ only)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
